MySQL- Steps
----------------
-- SYNTAX FOR  MySQL CREATE USER with PASSWORD
CREATE USER [IF NOT EXISTS] [User_Name]
    IDENTIFIED [BY/WITH] ['Password'];

step 1) to know complete account details =>   SELECT  user from  MYSQL.user; 

Step 2) to create accout ex : CREATE user  john@localhost IDENTIFIED by 'xxYYYxx';

step 3) to get all database details : SHOW   DATABASES;

step 4) CREATE DATABASE johndb;

step 5) use johndb;

step 6) GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES on johndb.* to john@localhost;


